videos.description: On a fast break, Kentavious Caldwell-Pope dishes to LeBron James, who lobs to Anthony Davis for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KCP, LeBron, AD connect on fast break alley-oop) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: KCP, LeBron, AD connect on fast break alley-oop

videos.description: Luka Doncic and Dorian Finney-Smith connect for a nice alley-oop dunk.

videos.description: During his warmup, Boban Marjanović takes a moment to wish everyone a Merry Christmas.
videos.headline: Boban's special Christmas message

videos.description: Kentavious Caldwell-Pope finds LeBron James on the fast-break for a smooth slam.

videos.description: As the first half expires, Kyle Kuzma dials in a 3-pointer to give the Lakers a 69-57 lead over the Mavericks.

videos.headline: Kuzma buries buzzer-beater to end first half

videos.description: LeBron James dances and dribbles before knocking down a step-back 3-pointer over Luka Doncic.

videos.description: LeBron James drops 22 points and 10 assists, while Anthony Davis scores 28 points with 8 rebounds in the Lakers' 138-115 Christmas Day win over the Mavericks.
